{"TopicId":157978,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Backspace doesn\u0026#039;t refocus the camera on the spacecraft. Any ideas?","CreatedByName":"SlabGizor117","CreatedById":135987,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T17:51:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SlabGizor117","CreatedById":135987,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T17:51:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTitle pretty much. \u00A0If I double click Kerbin then press Backspace it doesn\u0027t refocus on the craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T17:53:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHiya, its default binding is backquote now, it\u0027s left of the 1 key, hope this helps.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T18:00:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis one \u00A0~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Waxing_Kibbous","CreatedById":151611,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T18:05:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E you can change them in the keymap editor in settings, the offending shortcuts are in the vessel and game tabs. (I don\u0027t get why this change was made, who uses emergency abort in KSP enough to give it better real estate than refocus craft?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-20T18:07:04Z\u0022 title=\u002203/20/2017 06:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 20, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Waxing_Kibbous\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SlabGizor117","CreatedById":135987,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T18:09:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh well that\u0027s dumb. \u00A0KSP Wiki still says Backspace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: \u00A0Nevermind it does, just not clearly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-20T18:10:36Z\u0022 title=\u002203/20/2017 06:10  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 20, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by SlabGizor117\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T18:16:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell the KSP wiki could do with updating, it\u0027s user contributed \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBackspace to reset the camera conflicted with the Abort action group, so had to be changed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Foxster","CreatedById":113764,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T19:14:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222991845\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490033791\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n57 minutes ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell the KSP wiki could do with updating, it\u0027s user contributed \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBackspace to reset the camera conflicted with the Abort action group, so had to be changed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...and that\u0027s because hardly anyone uses the reset camera function and everyone is using the abort action all the time, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T19:18:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure your point, but there are times where reset camera and abort are both active, so having them on the same button was detrimental.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s remappable so knock yourself out and rebind it to backspace if you want.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBackquote is a little more ergonomic as it\u0027s near the tab key for cycling through bodies, shift\u002Btab to cycle backwards, it\u0027s also the key for search in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Foxster","CreatedById":113764,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T19:24:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry, was not well phrased.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat I meant was that if you had to move a function that everyone had got used to then didn\u0027t it make more sense to move the function that is much less well used i.e. abort?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I get your point that we can edit the key usage.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T19:29:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222991932\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490037884\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113764\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Foxster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Foxster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat I meant was that if you had to move a function that everyone had got used to then didn\u0027t it make more sense to move the function that is much less well used i.e. abort?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess, though I find my left hand on wasd, and my right hand on the mouse or joystick, comfortably away from the button that can wreck my flight if I hit it by mistake, which is also comfortably large and easy to jab when I do actually need it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo there\u0027s some logic to it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T19:50:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222991927\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490037483\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n32 minutes ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut there are times where reset camera and abort are both active, so having them on the same button was detrimental.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre there? I can\u0027t think of any.\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EHowever\u003C/em\u003E, I\u0027ve more than once attempted to hit backspace to re-center the flight camera, because of habit, with disastrous results, so I agree it was detrimental.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T19:51:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you flew in IVA, you\u0027d have run into this issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T21:54:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222991927\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490037483\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBackquote is a little more ergonomic as it\u0027s near the tab key for cycling through bodies, \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eshift\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u002Btab to cycle backwards, it\u0027s also the key for search in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kryxal","CreatedById":102688,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T22:01:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe backspace should have been moved ... but shift-tab is ALSO a danger if you have your navball up in map view.\u00A0 You just want to go back 1-2 celestial bodies, and suddenly you throttle up!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T18:04:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222992101\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490047270\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102688\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kryxal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, Kryxal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0... but shift-tab is ALSO a danger if you have your navball up in map view.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0 Or if you play through Steam. It\u0027s the Steam Overlay command for every game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T18:17:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, it could be changed, but to what?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Noobton","CreatedById":114094,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T18:25:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222992101\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490047270\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102688\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kryxal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, Kryxal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe backspace should have been moved ... but shift-tab is ALSO a danger if you have your navball up in map view.\u00A0 You just want to go back 1-2 celestial bodies, and suddenly you throttle up!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhuh so that\u0027s what\u0027s been throttling up my ships!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T22:13:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222992958\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490120222\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, it could be changed, but to what?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre right and left alt taken? \u00A0 Right cycles through planets\u00A0one way, left cycles through the other way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDangerously close to the spacebar, but no one ever said spaceflight was easy! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-21T22:14:14Z\u0022 title=\u002203/21/2017 10:14  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 21, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by klesh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T22:32:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222993099\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490134418\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre right and left alt taken?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLeft alt can\u0027t be used on Linux because the supported distro (Ubuntu) uses it as a special key, it allows you to grab and move an applications window without using the header bar for example.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight alt is a bit strange, it\u0027s really AltGr on many keyboards and Unity seems unable to detect it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"paulprogart","CreatedById":174587,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T23:09:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEhhh just make something like this mandatory for KSP:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00220xMdcPY.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/0xMdcPY.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProblem solved.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-22T18:22:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222993145\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490137782\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174587\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022paulprogart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, paulprogart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEhhh just make something like this mandatory for KSP:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/0xMdcPY.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00220xMdcPY.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/0xMdcPY.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProblem solved.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr one of those\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jfe2NLe.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/jfe2NLe.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-22T18:27:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSurely you jest.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022side-panel-collage.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.saitek.com/uk/imgs/product/farmsim-sidepanel/page/side-panel-collage.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-22T19:08:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo... how this update that bring a free game keyboard will be handled?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-23T02:10:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222993888\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490207250\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSurely you jest.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.saitek.com/uk/imgs/product/farmsim-sidepanel/page/side-panel-collage.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022side-panel-collage.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.saitek.com/uk/imgs/product/farmsim-sidepanel/page/side-panel-collage.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWowie zowie, that controller is only $150 usd on amazon. \u00A0 I might have to get that thing. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Saitek-Farm-Vehicle-Panel/dp/B01M1B2MJX\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Saitek-Farm-Vehicle-Panel/dp/B01M1B2MJX\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}